  <section class="main-section" id="Introduction">
    <header>Introduction</header>
    <article>
	<p>
This is a SAFETY DATA SHEET for Benzoic Acid according to Regulation (EC) No. 1907/2006.<br>
Version 6.4<br>
Revision Date 30.04.2021<br>
Print Date 27.11.2021<br>
GENERIC EU MSDS - NO COUNTRY SPECIFIC DATA - NO OEL DATA<br>
     </p>
    </article>
  </section>  
  
